title: The Mike Rosen Radio Show JAN-02-2014 THURS
description:
The Mike Rosen Radio Show JAN-02-2014 THURS






Thursday, January 02, 2014
The Day After Pot Legalization

 
 

 - 9AM hour

1. Yesterday was first day of the legal sale of marijuana. 
2. South Carolina congressman Trey Gowdy on the NY Times Benghazi story. 
3. People who move to Colorado just because pot is legal.



 - 10AM hour

1. More discussion of pot and those who use it. 
2. Judges' contrasting decisions on meta data mining by the NSA.



 - 11AM hour

Stupid letter to the editor of the day on teachers and the second amendment.
